        Installation
        ------------
        
        You can install "pytest-mypy" via `pip`_ from `PyPI`_::
        
            $ pip install pytest-mypy
        
            pyvenv venv
            source venv/bin/activate
            python setup.py develop
            venv/bin/py.test --mypy example_test.py
        
        
        
